from: Description Embrace a more technical and versatile style with the Fintoni Overshirt. This piece truly rides the line between a shirt and a jacket, giving you that perfect "shacket" feel. Crafted from a lightweight yet durable reipstop nylon, it has a fluid drape and isn't stiff, making it comfortable and easy to layer. The design features a double-ended zipper and a patch pocket, giving it a utility-inspired look. Long Sleeve Ripstop Fabrication With Water Repellent Finish Chest Patch Pocket Welt Side Pockets Full Length Double Ended Zipper Straight Hem Embroidered Gold F Fit Relaxed Fit Composition And Care 100% Recycled Nylon Machine Wash
